Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:54.11,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發信人：艾基爾 添加的通訊錄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:54.11,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主題：Look at this！！
